{"tid":1072501,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沈大師醒你炒8字頭股攻略","createTime":"2019-03-22T05:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T13:00:54.000Z","uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"66ba87eb9b598dbecaccbb5d70515e4d5c8a6a4b","tid":1072501,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"剛剛本報的周日導航，就提到創業板有機會成為「明日之升」，博其將來升級轉主板，到底八字頭的股份是否值博？<br />\n<br />\n訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈表示，並不是一定8字頭的股份就一定抗拒，第一可從市場對於殼價的估計，近期聽聞主板已叫價至4.8億元，而創業板就達2億以上，<br />\n「似乎內地不少民企都急於借殼上市，所以如果有創業板的股份的市值在1億或以下，可買少少用黎擺，好似係舊樓落釘，等佢爆升。」第二就是看業績，看其是否有能力由創業板升上主板，身價就會不同。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，名家國際（8108）、仁智國際（8082）及中國融保（8090）都可留意，因這些8字頭的股份不算升得多，或者個別可自行尋寶，最重要是看其市值大不大，而策略是以小博大，小注買5至6隻股份，只要買中一隻升幾倍，就足夠抵銷其他幾隻的成本，即使只得個「坐」字，都不會過於「綁死」資金。"},{"pid":"ea42b234bcd04bc7cd4a495dd229188b6c590d61","tid":1072501,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20130812/51636079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20130812%2F51636079&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=635af845\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20130812%2F51636079&h=3290cf2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20130812/51636079</a><br />\n<br />\n貼返link"},{"pid":"f4a85c43193fb6c5ae9c46312bef1a79cf592fd3","tid":1072501,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"撚有兩億殼價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c4252e59f962c13aa12427bb5fc3530e172db7","tid":1072501,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"果幾隻而家點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50ab92